{"tid":2487944,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"徐睿知遭爆把工作人員當狗！　「車內吸菸飆髒話」10霸道行徑","createTime":"2021-04-14T02:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T03:25:49.000Z","uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"fdf197b43863be963ac816e0bd8cfc180b5aa54c","tid":2487944,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:11:57.000Z","msg":"南韓演員徐睿知和金正賢的對話遭爆出，其中最讓韓網詫異的是「你不和工作人員打招呼是對的」，也因為這樣造成了人品議論。一名自稱曾與徐共事的工作人員（下稱A某）14日凌晨在Pann寫下長文，爆料對方完全不將工作人員當人看：「把我們當狗豬一樣藐視。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5564/d5564041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5564%2Fd5564041.jpg&h=671a1675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲徐睿知因金正賢事件遭連環爆出負面新聞。（圖／翻攝自GOLDMEDALIST）<br />\n<br />\nA某14日於Pann發文，標題寫下「曾共事的工作人員爆料演員徐睿知的人品」，文內指出徐睿知完全不管二手菸問題都會在車上抽菸，髒話掛嘴邊，不只如此只要她去哪工作人員就得跟上，如果她心情不好不吃飯，那工作人員也不能吃：「因為演員都沒吃了。」<br />\n<br />\n而且，A某在拍攝前一天被徐睿知緊抓著聊天不放，只睡了1、2個小時，隔天忍不住睡意就被罵，為了醒腦吃糖又被罵「妳算老幾竟敢在演員工作時吃糖果」。A某更指出徐睿知因為個性差，所以單拍一個作品就換了好幾個經紀人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5564/d5564040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5564%2Fd5564040.jpg&h=abb016eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲徐睿知遭爆常罵髒話還會在車內抽菸。（圖／翻攝自GOLDMEDALIST）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，A某也提到徐睿知非常自戀：「說是要愛自己負責的演員，要我們（工作人員）的手機桌布都放妳的照片，如果有妳的新聞就要我們去留言稱讚好漂亮、演技真好，還把我們的帳號背下來碎念『怎麼都寫一樣的，也寫點別的』，真的非常厭煩，而且還要我們加入妳的Fan Cafe，明明這麼愛自己，怎麼就沒辦法愛給身邊的人？」<br />\n<br />\n爆料文的最後，A某附上徐睿知在宣傳《另有他路》上《朴善英的Cinetown》的腳本，還有徐睿知的親筆簽名，她還強調：「（徐睿知）本身就很自戀，所以就算沒跟她要簽名也會自己簽（給工作人員）。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5564/d5564044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5564%2Fd5564044.jpg&h=2ffa1811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5564/d5564045.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5564%2Fd5564045.jpg&h=e350188f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲A某附上腳本和簽名以證明自己所言不假。（圖／翻攝自Pann）"},{"pid":"c557b41c5a3847076f11328de7f2d92b4a80b8a6","tid":2487944,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:12:45.000Z","msg":"原來佢咁壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf3d1df364ea51376574eef670941bb90027673","tid":2487944,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"衰女人...<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6ed08e82d63b16061fb805f0819b449709d0a2","tid":2487944,"uid":28913,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:13:59.000Z","msg":"條女睇樣都知係S 底<br />\n<br />\n快d點呼喝我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b9ffcb8c4dbb6e4c989e6b9f6406307fda0493","tid":2487944,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:16:21.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以屌我<br />\n點解無lala 爆單咁嘅嘢 唔似咁癲"},{"pid":"5a70d7578b0b98f3c308ccad6482aaf3f871f239","tid":2487944,"uid":33508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7b9ffcb8c4dbb6e4c989e6b9f6406307fda0493","tid":2487944,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:16:21.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以屌我<br />\n點解無lala 爆單咁嘅嘢 唔似咁癲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:17:26.000Z","msg":"就完約"},{"pid":"a16871202cb2846d988b93c1f53f260fd874e9d4","tid":2487944,"uid":294121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:18:27.000Z","msg":"好想條女扯完啖煙再吹d煙落我塊面到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bddf3f33cc9a2c6247c1872fd67415c5